title: 161: The New Year, New Food Finds Episode
itunes:title: The New Year, New Food Finds Episode
description: In this episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey are taste-testing some really yummy food finds like cauli’ bowls, oat milk soup, naan chips, refried beans, broccoli bites, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus the find of the episode: a brand new protein pancake mix from Kodiak Cakes! No time to waste—push play and then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for more info!
itunes:summary: HAPPY NEW YEAR! Let’s jump right in with new food finds for 2022!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
